<TD>IdentiKid understands the need to protect personal information from misuse, and respect everyone's right to privacy, therefore we have procedures in place for the protection of your personal information. 
<P>Our Privacy Policy covers the collection, use, storage and disclosure of personal information and complies with the National Privacy Principles. We are constantly monitoring all aspects of information usage to ensure your information is protected. 
<P>We strive to maintain an open and accountable policy on the privacy of personal information. We are available to discuss our policy or any queries with you. 
<P>For further details on the identiKid privacy policy contact;</P>
<P>Waldee&nbsp;Pty Ltd<BR>Tel - 1300 13 3949<BR></P>
<P><STRONG>Privacy Policy - (NPP5.1)</STRONG></P>
